    <para id="id2263024">To summarize, we have taken two arbitrary vectors, <m:math>
<m:mi>w</m:mi>
</m:math> and <m:math>
<m:mi>x</m:mi>
</m:math>, and decomposed
<m:math>
<m:mi>w</m:mi>
</m:math> into a component in the direction of 
<m:math>
<m:mi>x</m:mi>
</m:math> and a component orthogonal to 
<m:math>
<m:mi>x</m:mi>
</m:math>.
</para>
